title: Reshape Parametric Survival Data
newdatasetname: New dataset name (no spaces or special characters) to create a censored formatted dataset
label1: Select total units and select either failure or censor variable, or just select both failure and censor and leave total units empty
variableEventSelcted: Select the variable for event (e.g., failed)
variableCensorSelcted: Select the variable for censor (e.g., not failed)
variableTotalUnitsSelcted: Select total units only if one (not both) of failed or censored is selected above
variableSortingSelcted: (optional) Select a variable to sort the new dataset
